{"word":"G864 - ἀφικνέομαι - aphiknéomai - af-ik-neh'-om-ahee - Come abroad","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀφικνέομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">aphiknéomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">af-ik-neh'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Come abroad</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தெரியவா"},{"paragraph":"to come from a place, to come to, arrive at"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G2425 - ἱκανός - hikanós - hik-an-os'/2425\">G2425</a>; to <i>go</i> (that is, <i>spread</i>) <i>forth</i> (by rumor): - come abroad.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}